  5. Database Connection
  Connection settings are located in Kapsarc.College\Kapsarc.College\appsettings.json under the ConnectionStrings
  section. Look for the key umbracoDbDSN. Ensure the Server, Database, and Credentials match your local SQL Server
  instance.

